The paper discusses an algorithm for aligning large-scale knowledge bases, which involves database management (cs.DB), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), information retrieval (cs.IR), and natural language processing (cs.CL) techniques. The algorithm also leverages similarity measures between entity properties, which is a common approach in machine learning (cs.LG).
